<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ạ̉y bhjẗ lnạ wsrwr wʿzạ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ạảyũ bah̊jaẗiⁿ lanā
 wasurūriⁿ waʿazā
 biạlãdẖī ʿanãạ qaḍay̱
 wār̊taqay̱ ại̹lay̱ ạlsãmā

[V2]
 2- man̊ẓaru ạlrãbĩ ạl̊bahī̃̊
 bihi bah̊jaẗu ạl̊qulūb̊
 gẖaẙrahu lạ nasẖ̊tahī
 wabihi ạlnãf̊su taṭīb̊

[V3]
 3- fah̊wa kan̊zunā ạl̊gẖanī̃̊
 wah̊wa rā̊̉sunā ạl̊ḥabīb̊
 waʿani ạl̊ʿālami qad̊
 mut̊nā maʿ̊hu biạlṣãlīb̊

[V4]
 4- wabihi naṭ̊lubu mā
 faẘqu ḥaẙtẖu qad̊ jalas̊
 nab̊tagẖī ại̹r̊tẖaⁿạ lanā
 lạ yasẖūbuhu danas̊

[V5]
 5- fālãdẖī fī maj̊dihi
 bibahāhu nar̊tawī
 tārikīna mā warā
 ại̹dẖ̊ bihi lạ nan̊gẖawī

[V6]
 6- kaẙfa nab̊gẖī gẖaẙrahu
 wah̊wa gẖāyaẗu ạl̊munay̱
 qal̊bunā yaṣ̊bū lahu
 ḥubũhu yaḥ̊ṣurunā</lyrics>
</song>